  "tips": [
    {
      "type": "lead",
      "text": "No new keys today, and very nearly the end of the road. Everything you have built comes down to one thing here: an even tempo, held without strain, at full speed. Three words, one steady pace."
    },
    {
      "type": "drop",
      "text": "Hands on the home row, thumbs over the space bar, eyes off the keys. Repeat each word without forcing it. If the pace wavers, count it back into line: one, two, three, four."
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "icon": "metronome",
      "title": "Even hands",
      "text": "At this speed, speed is no longer the question - control is. Keep one gap between keystrokes and the rest takes care of itself. The hand that stays even at a hundred is a hand you can trust on any page."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": "lessons lessons lessons lessons lessons",
      "finger": "blue",
      "title": "Rhythm: lessons",
      "hint": "Repeat at one tempo: lessons - lessons - lessons. Hold the gaps equal."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": "perspective perspective perspective",
      "finger": "pink",
      "title": "Rhythm: perspective",
      "hint": "Repeat steadily, no jerks: perspective - perspective - perspective."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": "tempo tempo tempo tempo",
      "finger": "blue",
      "title": "Rhythm: tempo",
      "hint": "Repeat evenly: tempo - tempo - tempo. Do not speed up at the end."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Let the hand take each word whole and let your thought run ahead, unbothered. Even repetition is what carried you this far, one steady pass at a time. Hold that pace and the last lesson is already half won."
    },
    {
      "type": "pullquote",
      "text": "Loosen your shoulders and wrists, picture the metronome, and let rhythm hold the speed. A little every day brought you here.",
      "by": "Eleanor Hayes, editor"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "All three done? Open the trainer below and take one clean run at the full lesson text. That run saves your progress and unlocks the next lesson."
    }
  ],
